				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I know how to do solo HOs. And I know how to do an HO with my partner.  What I do not understand is how to do an HO with more than two folks.
<br />

<br />
What is with the multiple people HOs?
<br />

<br />
I start chain, he completes: we have a wheel with two icons. We follow the icons; wheel finished.
<br />

<br />
What am I missing?
<br />

<br />
thanks!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
